    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It has been my absolute pride and joy, and I've kept it in total showroom condition\u2014not a single scratch, dent, or speck of dust anywhere! It drives like an absolute dream and still smells brand new. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I\u2019m looking for a new owner who will love it just as much as I do. Drop me a message and let's get you in the driver's seat!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
